SORRY.

10:23.890 --> 10:27.792
- YOU ALL WANT TO DO
SOME OF THAT GOD DRUG?

10:27.794 --> 10:31.129
[violin screeching eerily]

10:31.131 --> 10:34.165
♪ ♪

10:34.167 --> 10:34.933
- NO.

10:34.935 --> 10:36.034
- WHAT THE [bleep]?

10:36.036 --> 10:36.768
- WHO'S THIS GUY?

10:36.770 --> 10:39.437
- YOU ALL EVER HEARD
OF THE GOD DRUG?

10:39.439 --> 10:42.574
- I'VE--I'VE NEVER
HEARD OF THAT.

10:42.576 --> 10:46.144
- AKA SLAYER, CUTTY-CUTTY,

10:46.146 --> 10:52.050
DOUBLE CUTTY, ELMO, CAT VAG.

10:52.052 --> 10:52.751
- OKAY.

10:52.753 --> 10:55.720
- LONG ISLAND BRAIN SLICE,

10:55.722 --> 10:57.188
FUNT.

10:57.190 --> 10:58.356
- FUNT?
- FUNT.

10:58.358 --> 10:59.524
- FUNT, I'VE HEARD OF THAT.

10:59.526 --> 11:04.195
- IT TAKES ALL YOUR GREATEST
FEARS AND INSECURITIES,

11:04.197 --> 11:07.632
AND IT GIVES THEM
TEETH AND ARMS,

11:07.634 --> 11:10.602
AND THEN IT LOCKS YOU
IN A ROOM WITH THEM

11:10.604 --> 11:14.339
FROM WHICH YOU CANNOT ESCAPE.

11:16.509 --> 11:17.475
- OH, THAT SOUNDS TERRIBLE.

11:17.477 --> 11:20.478
- YEAH, I DON'T WANT THAT, MAN.
- NONE OF THOSE WORDS ARE GOOD.

11:20.480 --> 11:23.715
- YOU REALIZE THE FACE OF GOD

11:23.717 --> 11:26.851
IS SOMEWHERE INSIDE YOUR BODY,

11:26.853 --> 11:31.656
BUT YOU CAN'T FIND IT,
AND IT HATES YOU.

11:31.658 --> 11:34.726
- UM, OKAY, NONE OF US ARE
INTERESTED IN THIS DRUG.

11:34.728 --> 11:35.894
THANK YOU, SIR.
NICE MEETING YOU.

11:35.896 --> 11:37.896
- LET'S HEAR HIM OUT.
LET'S HEAR HIM OUT.

11:37.898 --> 11:43.334
- IT'S A RAZOR SHARP CRYSTAL
YOU TUCK UNDER YOUR EYELID.

11:43.336 --> 11:44.235
- OOH.
- UGH.

11:44.237 --> 11:48.506
- AND THEN WHEN YOUR OCULAR
CAVITY STARTS BLEEDING,

11:48.508 --> 11:50.975
IT GOES DIRECTLY
INTO YOUR BRAIN.

11:50.977 --> 11:53.378
- I FEEL LIKE
THERE'S GOT TO BE A GOOD PART.

11:53.380 --> 11:54.946
- YEAH, YOU'VE JUST DESCRIBED

11:54.948 --> 11:58.583
A LIFE-WRECKING
PHYSICAL ADDICTION.

11:58.585 --> 12:00.752
- IF YOU'D LET HIM FINISH--
IF YOU'D LET HIM FINISH,

12:00.754 --> 12:03.288
HE'S GONNA GET TO
THE EUPHORIA, I'M SURE.

12:03.290 --> 12:07.258
- JUST WHEN YOU CAN'T TAKE
ANY MORE,

12:07.260 --> 12:08.226
[inhales sharply]

12:08.228 --> 12:09.427
YOU POOP YOUR MOUTH.

12:09.429 --> 12:11.763
- I'M SORRY, WHAT?
- YOU POOP IN YOUR MOUTH?

12:11.765 --> 12:13.298
- NO,

12:13.300 --> 12:15.300
YOU POOP OUT OF YOUR MOUTH.

12:15.302 --> 12:16.835
- I'M IN.

12:16.837 --> 12:19.003
GUYS, IF PEOPLE WILL
REALLY GO THROUGH THIS,

12:19.005 --> 12:20.171
THE HIGH MUST BE AMAZING.

12:20.173 --> 12:21.973
- BUDDY,
REMEMBER WHEN YOU DID MUSHROOMS

12:21.975 --> 12:23.074
AND YOU CRIED FOR THREE HOURS?

12:23.076 --> 12:24.609
THIS IS WORSE THAN THAT.
- YEAH.

12:24.611 --> 12:26.544
- OH, THE EYES.

12:26.546 --> 12:28.513
OH, OH!

12:28.515 --> 12:29.714
[yelling]

12:29.716 --> 12:31.916
OH, GOD!

12:31.918 --> 12:33.051
[both groaning]
- IT HURTS!

12:33.053 --> 12:35.820
- OH, JEB.
- OH, THAT HURTS!

12:35.822 --> 12:38.056
WHEN DOES IT START WORKING?

12:38.058 --> 12:39.858
- HOW SHOULD I KNOW?

12:39.860 --> 12:42.360
I DON'T DO DRUGS.

12:42.928 --> 12:45.130
DRUGS ARE FOR LOSERS.

13:07.853 --> 13:10.321
THIS IS HIM.

13:10.323 --> 13:11.156
YEAH, THIS IS HIM.

13:11.158 --> 13:13.625
- WELL, I'M VERY SORRY, SIR.

13:13.627 --> 13:16.661
- HOLD ON A SECOND.

13:16.663 --> 13:19.297
WAIT.

13:19.299 --> 13:20.598
IS THIS HIM?

13:20.600 --> 13:21.866
- OH, TAKE YOUR TIME, SIR.

13:21.868 --> 13:23.401
THERE'S NO RUSH.

13:23.403 --> 13:25.703
- YES, YES, YES,
IT'S DEFINITELY HIM.

13:25.705 --> 13:28.406
- OKAY,
SO IF YOU MAKE YOUR WAY--

13:28.408 --> 13:30.241
- WAIT.

13:30.243 --> 13:34.045
IT SEEMS LIKE HIM.

13:34.047 --> 13:39.284
YES, YES,
IT VERY MUCH COULD BE HIM.

13:40.352 --> 13:42.554
- [clears throat]
SO THIS--THIS IS HIM?

13:42.556 --> 13:47.458
- ALTHOUGH...HMM.

13:47.460 --> 13:49.227
LET ME JUST--

13:54.300 --> 13:55.099
- OKAY, I'M SORRY.

13:55.101 --> 13:56.067
SIR, I KNOW THAT YOU'RE BLIND,

13:56.069 --> 13:57.669
BUT YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO MAKE
A DECISION.

13:57.671 --> 13:59.804
- OH, I'M NOT BLIND.

13:59.806 --> 14:01.973
- OH, THANK GOD.
[chuckles]

14:01.975 --> 14:04.175
I'M NOT A MORTICIAN.

14:04.177 --> 14:05.009
- AND I'M NOT DEAD,

14:05.011 --> 14:09.080
BUT PLEASE DON'T STOP
ON MY ACCOUNT.

14:18.991 --> 14:21.125
- SHH.

14:21.127 --> 14:26.598
- IT'S DEFINITELY NOT HIM.

14:26.600 --> 14:28.466
- HONESTLY, MAKE A WISH,

14:28.468 --> 14:31.903
KIND OF A BRILLIANT
CHARITY IDEA,

14:31.905 --> 14:36.407
BECAUSE REALLY, I MEAN,
IT JUST LOOKS REAL GOOD.

14:36.409 --> 14:37.342
IT LOOKS REAL GOOD.

14:37.344 --> 14:39.544
THEY GET DONATIONS
OUT THEIR ASS, MAKE A WISH.

14:39.546 --> 14:41.145
- MY THING IS, I WONDER IF
THE MAKE A WISH PEOPLE, LIKE--

14:41.147 --> 14:43.514
IT'S LIKE, "OH, I'M GONNA GO
PARASAILING WITH YOU."

14:43.516 --> 14:44.515
- RIGHT.
- THAT'S MY ONLY THING.

14:44.517 --> 14:46.751
I'M LIKE, "WAIT A MINUTE,
DO YOU GET TO GO WITH THE KID?"

14:46.753 --> 14:48.920
- "I THOUGHT YOU JUST
ORGANIZED THE WISHES, BUT"--

14:48.922 --> 14:50.521
- "AND THEN YOU WENT BACK
TO YOUR OFFICE.

14:50.523 --> 14:51.923
WHY ARE YOU UP IN THERE
PARASAILING?"

14:51.925 --> 14:54.058
- "WHY ARE YOU GOING FIRST?
WHAT THE HELL?

14:54.060 --> 14:54.759
I'M THE KID."

14:54.761 --> 14:55.994
- "ARE YOU SURE
THAT THIS KID'S WISH

14:55.996 --> 15:00.231
WAS TO GO TO THE BIKINI CONTEST
AT CARNIVAL IN BRAZIL?"

15:00.233 --> 15:02.267
THEY COULD BE MAKING THAT UP.
- WHO KNOWS, RIGHT?

15:02.269 --> 15:04.502
I'M NOT GONNA JUST START
GIVING ALL MY MONEY

15:04.504 --> 15:08.506
TO PEOPLE I DON'T KNOW, RIGHT?

15:08.508 --> 15:10.041
I MEAN, THAT DOESN'T--
- RIGHT.

15:10.043 --> 15:12.443
WELL, THAT'S--

15:12.445 --> 15:14.379
THAT'S CHARITY.

15:16.248 --> 15:17.515
[monitor beeping steadily]

15:17.517 --> 15:20.652
[thunder booming]

15:20.654 --> 15:23.988
- HI, YOU MUST BE LIAM.

15:23.990 --> 15:27.959
- HEY, BUDDY,
HOW ARE YOU FEELING TODAY?

15:27.961 --> 15:32.096
- [hoarsely]
I'M FEELING FINE, DR. GUPTA.

15:32.098 --> 15:33.798
JUST FINE.

15:33.800 --> 15:34.832
- THIS IS MARION GLASS,

15:34.834 --> 15:37.468
AND SHE'S FROM
THE MAKE A WISH FOUNDATION.

15:37.470 --> 15:39.938
- MARION GLASS.

15:39.940 --> 15:42.407
- HOW ARE YOU
FEELING TODAY, LIAM?

15:42.409 --> 15:46.110
- I'M FINE, MARION GLASS.
- GOOD.

15:46.112 --> 15:48.413
WELL, I HAVE SOME NEWS
THAT MIGHT MAKE YOU FEEL

15:48.415 --> 15:49.747
A LITTLE BETTER, HUH?

15:49.749 --> 15:52.817
WE AT THE MAKE A WISH FOUNDATION
MAKE DREAMS COME TRUE

15:52.819 --> 15:57.922
FOR LITTLE BOYS AND LITTLE GIRLS
WHO ARE VERY SICK JUST LIKE YOU.

15:57.924 --> 16:03.328
- THERE ARE NO CHILDREN
LIKE ME, MARION GLASS.

16:03.330 --> 16:04.896
- OH, OF COURSE NOT.

16:04.898 --> 16:07.832
YOU'RE ONE OF A KIND,
BUT WE'RE GONNA MAKE ANY DREAM

16:07.834 --> 16:10.935
COME TRUE
THAT YOU COULD EVER HAVE, OKAY?

16:10.937 --> 16:11.970
- ANYTHING?

16:11.972 --> 16:14.172
- THAT'S RIGHT, BUDDY.
THAT'S RIGHT.

16:14.174 --> 16:18.242
WOULD YOU LIKE TO PLAY WITH
YOUR FAVORITE BASKETBALL TEAM?

16:20.079 --> 16:23.514
WHAT ABOUT BE SUPERMAN
FOR A DAY?

16:23.516 --> 16:26.751
- I WISH TO DROWN A MAN.

16:26.753 --> 16:29.887
[eerie music]

16:29.889 --> 16:30.888
♪ ♪

16:30.890 --> 16:31.522
- WHAT?

16:31.524 --> 16:35.493
- TO DROWN A MAN IN THE BATHTUB.

16:35.495 --> 16:38.596
TO HOLD HIM DOWN
WHILE THE LAST BREATH

16:38.598 --> 16:43.434
ESCAPES HIS BODY,
AND THEN BATHE IN THAT WATER,

16:43.436 --> 16:45.169
ALL THE WHILE SINGING,

16:45.171 --> 16:49.207
♪ LA-LA, LA-LA ♪

16:49.209 --> 16:51.676
♪ LA-LA, LA ♪

16:51.678 --> 16:53.745
- LIAM.

16:53.747 --> 16:56.147
- YOU SAID ANYTHING.

16:56.149 --> 17:00.051
- WELL, S-SURELY WE DON'T WANT
TO HURT OTHER PEOPLE,

17:00.053 --> 17:01.519
NOW, DO WE, KIDDO?

17:01.521 --> 17:02.653
[both laugh uneasily]

17:02.655 --> 17:03.588
ANYTHING ELSE?

17:03.590 --> 17:07.158
FLY IN A HOT AIR BALLOON
OR MEET A CELEBRITY?

17:07.160 --> 17:11.963
- MY NEW WISH IS TO LEAN OVER
THE BODY OF A DYING MAN

17:11.965 --> 17:17.101
AND PUT MY LIPS ON HIS,
STEALING HIS LAST BREATH.

17:17.103 --> 17:18.436
[inhales]

17:18.438 --> 17:19.337
- LIAM.

17:19.339 --> 17:21.539
- NO ONE WILL GET HURT.

17:21.541 --> 17:22.607
- ABSOLUTELY NOT.

17:22.609 --> 17:24.242
I DON'T EVEN KNOW WHERE YOU--

17:24.244 --> 17:28.212
- I WISH TO TAKE
ALL THE PROSTHETIC LEGS

17:28.214 --> 17:32.483
IN THE HOSPITAL
AND BIND THEM TOGETHER

17:32.485 --> 17:35.553
WITH THE DRIED FLESH
OF THE DEAD

17:35.555 --> 17:41.592
INTO A WEBBED MASSIVE CREATURE,
AND--

17:41.594 --> 17:42.860
- LIAM!

17:42.862 --> 17:45.663
I AM SO SORRY, MS. GLASS.
- IT'S ALL RIGHT.

17:45.665 --> 17:47.865
HE--HE DOESN'T KNOW
WHAT HE'S SAYING.

17:47.867 --> 17:49.867
- I WISH TO PEE
IN YOUR MOUTH.

17:49.869 --> 17:51.936
- WHAT?
- BOTH OF YOU.

17:51.938 --> 17:52.670
- MINE?

17:52.672 --> 17:54.405
- ESPECIALLY YOU.
- OH.

17:54.407 --> 17:58.176
- I WISH TO PEE
IN BOTH OF YOUR MOUTHS

17:58.178 --> 17:59.410
AS I STAND OVER YOU.

17:59.412 --> 18:02.447
I'LL NEED A GLASS OF WATER
IN TEN MINUTES.

18:02.449 --> 18:03.981
- ENOUGH,
YOU LITTLE [bleep]!

18:03.983 --> 18:05.416
- DR. GUPTA!

18:05.418 --> 18:06.784
- NO.

18:06.786 --> 18:08.086
YOU ARE REPREHENSIBLE.

18:08.088 --> 18:10.054
YOU ARE EVIL.

18:10.056 --> 18:12.156
YOU ARE A DEVIL CHILD.

18:12.158 --> 18:13.124
- [whimpering]

18:13.126 --> 18:15.359
- DR. GUPTA,
HE'S NOT A DEVIL CHILD.

18:15.361 --> 18:16.494
HE'S JUST A CHILD.

18:16.496 --> 18:18.696
YOU HAVE NO BUSINESS WORKING
IN A PEDIATRIC WARD.

18:18.698 --> 18:20.832
- WHAT?
- I'M GONNA REPORT YOU.

18:20.834 --> 18:23.334
- [crying]

18:23.336 --> 18:24.702
[door slams]

18:26.305 --> 18:30.975
- ♪ SHAME ON YOU, GUPTA ♪

18:30.977 --> 18:35.246
♪ SHAME ON YOU, GUPTA ♪

18:35.248 --> 18:39.317
YOU REALLY UPSET
MARION GLASS.

18:39.319 --> 18:43.588
- THIS IS INSANE.

18:43.590 --> 18:46.390
YOU'VE MADE ME QUESTION
EVERYTHING THAT I'VE EVER

18:46.392 --> 18:51.662
BELIEVED ABOUT THE
ESSENTIAL GOODNESS OF CHILDREN.

18:51.664 --> 18:57.034
- WISH GRANTED.

18:57.036 --> 19:00.838
[flatlining]

19:12.684 --> 19:15.820
- [gasps]
- [giggles]

19:15.822 --> 19:17.421
I AM DYING THOUGH.

19:17.423 --> 19:19.257
[flatlining]

19:27.432 --> 19:31.002
[monitor beeping steadily]

19:31.870 --> 19:32.870
- HI, QUENTIN.

19:32.872 --> 19:33.905
- OH, DOCTOR.

19:33.907 --> 19:36.040
- I JUST WANTED TO REPORT
THAT THE SURGERY WENT OFF

19:36.042 --> 19:38.976
WITHOUT A HITCH
AND THAT YOUR HEART TRANSPLANT

19:38.978 --> 19:40.444
WAS A COMPLETE SUCCESS.

19:40.446 --> 19:44.615
- OH, I'M SO HAPPY
TO BE ALIVE.

19:44.617 --> 19:45.650
- I BET.
I BET.

19:45.652 --> 19:47.518
WELL, THANKFULLY
THE AFFORDABLE HEALTH CARE ACT

19:47.520 --> 19:49.520
ALLOWED YOU TO BE INSURED
AND PUT ON A DONOR LIST

19:49.522 --> 19:51.889
EVEN WITH YOUR
PREEXISTING CONDITIONS.

19:51.891 --> 19:55.526
- I'M TRULY,
TRULY THANKFUL.

19:55.528 --> 19:57.762
- THIS IS AN INSTANCE OF
OBAMACARE

19:57.764 --> 19:59.630
LITERALLY SAVING A LIFE.

19:59.632 --> 20:01.832
- OBAMACARE?

20:01.834 --> 20:03.167
OH, NO, YOU DON'T.

20:03.169 --> 20:08.839
YOU ARE NOT PUTTING
BIG GOVERNMENT INTO MY BODY.

20:08.841 --> 20:10.808
[yells]

20:10.810 --> 20:13.711
[grunting]

20:13.713 --> 20:14.612
- UGH.

20:14.614 --> 20:16.847
- [laughing]

20:16.849 --> 20:20.351
- OH!
- [groaning]

20:23.822 --> 20:26.490
[laughing]

20:26.492 --> 20:29.827
[flatlining]

20:30.329 --> 20:33.664
- UM, COULD--
COULD YOU GO GET ME SOME ICE?

20:33.666 --> 20:37.335
WE SHOULD PROBABLY
SAVE THIS.

20:43.041 --> 20:43.841
BUT WHAT SCARES YOU?

20:43.843 --> 20:45.610
BECAUSE, I MEAN, I KNOW THAT
YOU'RE A CONNOISSEUR.

20:45.612 --> 20:49.080
I KNOW THAT YOU GET SCARED,
BUT YOU'RE ALSO A CONNOISSEURS.

20:49.082 --> 20:53.184
- MM...

20:53.685 --> 20:56.687
POVERTY.
- [chuckles]

20:56.689 --> 20:59.156
- THE INJUSTICES OF
THE REAL WORLD.

20:59.158 --> 21:00.024
- OH, MY GOD.

21:00.026 --> 21:02.493
- ♪ I'M GONNA DO
MY ONE LINE HERE ♪

21:02.495 --> 21:04.829
- OH, YEAH.

21:08.300 --> 21:09.400
- WHY DON'T YOU JUST LEAVE
YOUR CAR

21:09.402 --> 21:11.669
IN THE OTHER PARKING LOT,
COME OVER TO MY HOUSE.

21:11.671 --> 21:12.570
WE BUILD A PILLOW FORT.

21:12.572 --> 21:14.839
YOU SPEND THE NIGHT,
AND WE WATCH A WHOLE BUNCH

21:14.841 --> 21:16.440
OF ANIMATED MUSICALS
AND WHATNOT.

21:16.442 --> 21:17.275
- OH, YOU GOT<i> HAPPY FEET</i>

21:17.277 --> 21:18.442
AND SOME JUICY JUICE,
WE GOT A DEAL.

21:18.444 --> 21:19.510
- OH, YOU KNOW
WE GOT THAT [bleep] NOW.

21:19.512 --> 21:20.978
AND A LITTLE BIT--
YOU KNOW, A LITTLE SOMETHING--

21:20.980 --> 21:21.011
THERE WE GO.
THERE WE GO, DOG.
